{"id": "27920", "post": "<div class=\"post-27920 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-datacenter tag-hardware tag-millenial-host tag-mlnl-host tag-tesla tag-ups\" id=\"post-27920\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/lowendtalk-member-creates-homemade-datacenter-ups-out-of-tesla-batteries/\" rel=\"bookmark\">LowEndTalk Member Creates Homemade Datacenter UPS Out of Tesla Batteries</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/datacenter/\" rel=\"tag\">datacenter</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/hardware/\" rel=\"tag\">hardware</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/millenial-host/\" rel=\"tag\">millenial.host</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/mlnl-host/\" rel=\"tag\">mlnl.host</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/tesla/\" rel=\"tag\">tesla</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/ups/\" rel=\"tag\">ups</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> August 5, 2021 @ 12:00 pm, by raindog308</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/battery_power_icon.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignright size-full wp-image-27921 litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/battery_power_icon.png\" alt=\"Battery Power Icon\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" align=\"right\" hspace=\"20\" data-srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/battery_power_icon.png 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/battery_power_icon-150x150.png 150w\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" srcset=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/battery_power_icon.png 300w, https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/battery_power_icon-150x150.png 150w\" data-was-processed=\"true\">Long-time community member @randvegeta has been sharing the story of his Lithium-powered datacenter UPS setup on LowEndTalk.&nbsp; He is the proprietor of <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/let-the-generational-wars-begin-millenial-host-tires-of-their-misspelled-name-rebrands-as-mlnl-host/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"mlnl.host\">MLNL.host</a>, a cheap VPS provider we featured yesterday.</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/167261/lithium-ion-ups/p1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"LowEndTalk\">Lithium Ion UPS</a> (October 2020)</li><li><a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/172977/diy-tesla-ups\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"LowEndTalk\">DIY Tesla UPS</a> (July 2021)</li></ul><p>As a quick overview for those who don\u2019t get down to the hardware layer much, a typical datacenter power setup looks like this:</p><ul><li>Main power comes in from the local utility company .</li><li>In the event this power fails, a UPS (uninterruptible power supply) kicks in and a diesel-powered generator is fired up.&nbsp; The UPS system is typically battery-based and are the size of small cars.</li><li>The UPS may have as little as 15 minutes of run time.&nbsp; Its function is to bridge power needs until the generator begin supplying electricity, which usually can occur in 60 seconds or less.</li></ul><p>@randvegeta\u2019s approach is a little different.&nbsp; He\u2019s using Tesla batteries.&nbsp; In contrast to the lead-acid-based UPSes in common use, he\u2019s hoping this setup will last 10 years or more.</p><p>It\u2019s an interesting mad-scientist kind of story and he\u2019s updated the community with pictures of his setup.&nbsp; Check the <a href=\"https://www.lowendtalk.com/discussion/172977/diy-tesla-ups\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" aria-label=\"LowEndTalk\">latest update</a>!&nbsp; @randvegata, please keep us up to date on your project.</p><div class=\"relpost-thumb-wrapper\"><div class=\"relpost-thumb-container\"><h3>Related posts:</h3><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div style=\"clear: both\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-container\"><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/let-the-generational-wars-begin-millenial-host-tires-of-their-misspelled-name-rebrands-as-mlnl-host/\"><div class=\"relpost-custom-block-single\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"mlnl.host\" style=\"background: transparent url(https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/mlnl-host-150x150.png) no-repeat scroll 0% 0%; width: 150px; height: 150px;\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-single-text\" style=\"font-family: Arial;  font-size: 12px;  color: #333333;\">Let the Generational Wars Begin: Millenial.Host Tires of Their Misspelled Name, Rebrands as MLNL.Hos...</div></div></a><a class=\"relpost-block-single\" href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/fire-damages-webnx-utah-datacenter-causes-extended-outage/\"><div class=\"relpost-custom-block-single\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 215px;\"><div class=\"relpost-block-single-image\" alt=\"Fire Damages WebNX Utah Datacenter, Causes Extended Outage\" style=\"background: transparent url(https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/datacenter-fire-150x150.png) no-repeat scroll 0% 0%; width: 150px; height: 150px;\"></div><div class=\"relpost-block-single-text\" style=\"font-family: Arial;  font-size: 12px;  color: #333333;\">Fire Damages WebNX Utah Datacenter, Causes Extended Outage</div></div></a></div><div style=\"clear: both\"></div></div></div><div id=\"author-bio-box\" style=\"background: #f8f8f8; border-top: 2px solid #cccccc; border-bottom: 2px solid #cccccc; 